com.pranavpandey.android.dynamic.support.widget

Class Dynamic

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pranavpandey.android.dynamic.support.widget.Dynamic

  • public class Dynamic
extends Object
    Helper class to manipulate inflated views at runtime according to their implemented types.

    These methods are provided to avoid any exceptions when views are replaced by the DynamicLayoutInflater. So, this is the recommended way to modify any of the following view types at runtime.

    See Also:
    DynamicWidget, DynamicBackgroundWidget, DynamicCornerWidget, DynamicLinkWidget, DynamicScrollableWidget, DynamicStateWidget, DynamicStateSelectedWidget, DynamicTextWidget
